headline: The Year’s Biggest Deal Could Yield a Record Payout for Bank of America
summary: The bank stands to earn $130 million for work on the railroad megadeal between Union Pacific and Norfolk Southern.

headline: Trump: Union Pacific, Norfolk Southern merger “sounds good to me”
summary: President Donald Trump said that the proposed merger of Union Pacific and Norfolk Southern forming the first U.S. transcontinental railroad “sounds good to me.” The post Trump: Union Pacific, Norfolk Southern merger “sounds good to me” appeared first on FreightWaves.
